description: This Portland cart is a favorite among Mexican food lovers. Customers go crazy for their handmade tortillas that are thick and soft and wrap perfectly around your choice of meat (hint: if you like pork, the carnitas and al pastor are must try items). Their menu also includes many more Mexican classics like burritos, tortas, enchiladas, tostadas, quesadillas, sopes, nachos and more.
name: Taqueria Lindo Michoacan
